title: Volcano erupts in Pacific, West Coast under tsunami advisory
content:
1. Volcano erupts in Pacific, West Coast under tsunami advisory  Associated Press
  2. Tsunami advisory in effect for US as waves hit Tonga following volcanic eruption  CNN
  3. Dramatic footage of tsunami hitting the Pacific island of Tonga after a giant underwater volcano erupted  Yahoo! Voices
  4. Tsunami Advisory in place on the US West coast following a Massive Volcanic Eruption  First Coast News
  5. Tsunami Advisory Updated: Evacuations At Santa Cruz Harbor, Berkeley Marina; Waves Surging On Ocean Beaches  CBS San Francisco
